body_html: I had exactly the same issue. I spend the entire day trying to figure out what was wrong. I installed and uninstalled python, tf, etc.. million times on my new Windows 10 machine. This morning I saw this post. I deleted protobuf 3.6.1 and installed 3.6.0. Bingo ! everything is working. Thanks a lot
